Package: lmmix
Title: Linear Mixed Models with Correlated Residuals
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Aurélien", "Nicosia", ,
           "116816597+AurelienNicosiaULaval@users.noreply.github.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fits Gaussian linear mixed models by explicitly optimizing the
    maximum likelihood or restricted maximum likelihood criterion. Random
    effects and correlated residual structures can be combined in the same
    model. Fixed-effect inference includes Satterthwaite and Kenward-Roger
    denominator degrees of freedom, type III tests, likelihood-ratio model
    comparisons, and estimated marginal means.
